y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貓貓真係好敏感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"我依家係將細貓困籠<br />\n因為想大貓可以自由咁周圍去<br />\n比佢知道佢先係呢間屋最大<br />\n可以比大貓慢慢習慣細貓既存在"},{"pid":"6d9a8b30c2e59822e3101dd5f09d1ccbc67a4790","tid":1592751,"uid":275030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27d8a2e1bf9a4f65680dbe246b12bd07bb737d57","tid":1592751,"uid":211157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bed98cc58b0e2997fa3f52ce9f750f76cd41ccd","tid":1592751,"uid":275030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dce340156bda650901d9da5918db91d0f202ab5","tid":1592751,"uid":211157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"有冇籠呀?<br />\n我依家都面對差唔多情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"有房 細貓困細房<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貓貓真係好敏感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"我依家係將細貓困籠<br />\n因為想大貓可以自由咁周圍去<br />\n比佢知道佢先係呢間屋最大<br />\n可以比大貓慢慢習慣細貓既存在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"我直頭教過大貓打細貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢比人搶野要反擊 <br />\n唉寧願佢地打下交"},{"pid":"afb6728c99ed78ecc765b3806af23c4c1e359baf","tid":1592751,"uid":321724,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"37ed38bec7af06dee25d85f28fa4eec4a71198eb","tid":1592751,"uid":196485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:25:17.000Z","msg":"細貓困籠 比大貓食野先 大貓食完先到細貓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"屋企貓貓本身自住左10年<br />\n上年接左兩隻貓貓番黎<br />\n兩隻貓住左一年籠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXGyJi1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXGyJi1.png&h=b7d94b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三層籠<